egistered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFFFF>3/20/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFFFF>7:51:09 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Where is the paladin's dragon/god weapon ??</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Every class has a &quot;penacle&quot; weapon/item coming from the dragons/gods or other unique &quot;boss&quot; MOB except paladins. Lets look at this on a per class/item basis.<br>
<br>
Warriors: Bloodfire, Soulleech, Sunderfury, Monsoon, Spined Dragon Claws, Ashenbone Warhammer<br>
Shadowknights: Bloodmoon, Soulleech, Beckon<br>
Rangers: Mistwalker, Briarzephyr<br>
Bards: Six-Note Blade, Evensong, Dawnchaser<br>
Rogues: Crystalline Spear, Gold Plated Koshigatana, Bone Razor, Vexthorne<br>
Monks: Rakusha Cloak, Sode of Empowerment, Basoon Haste Gauntlets<br>
Druids: Mistwalker, Heirophant's Crook, Staff of the Earthcrafter, Tunarian Scimitar<br>
Clerics: Dawnfire, Staff of Forbidden Rites, Truesight Hammer<br>
Shamans: Gardash, Barbarian Spiritists Hammer, Blight, Hammer of the Scourge, Withered Totem of Widdershins <br>
Wizards: Diamond Rod<br>
Necros: Staff of Undead Legions<br>
Enchanters: Rod of Unbound Thought<br>
Magicians: Staff of Elemental Mastery: Earth<br>
<br>
And Casters get the robes and other items such as...<br>
Crimson Robe of Alendine, Tobrin's Mystic Eyepatch, Amulet of Necropotence, Orb of Tishan, and even a few class specific weapons<br>
<br>
Paladins: Shield of the Immaculate, Shield of Stalwart Seas <br>
<br>
<br>
Someone correct me in that there is not 1 single Paladin only weapon that drops from a dragon or god!! And dont anyone come running to me with the Fiery Avenger. It requires TWO RARE DROPS off these mobs just to get PART OF THE QUEST, when other classes get their reward right from the mob itself, not to mention that the Ashenbone Warhammer has a better dmg/delay ratio. And if this isnt bad enough, the only thing that the god/dragons do drop for paladins is a shield(and only 1 can be used by all paladins), and since they nerfed the sprinkler drop, what are we supposed to use with the shield ??? Ghoulbane ???  Sheesh.... Why Verant?? What were you thinking ???<br>
<br>
Rone Darkbane<br>
50th Paladin - Karana</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#666666><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Vermilion Starfires</FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Unregistered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFFFF>3/20/00</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FFFFFF>7:56:19 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Um...Zephyrwind...and the other TWO POS swords</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Granted they are not doable till the exp, but that is only 3 or 4 weeks away.  Just relax and wait.<br>
